### Admin HTTP tests

@base=http://localhost:8000
@json=application/json
@token=YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### List users
GET {{base}}/api/admin/users
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get user details
GET {{base}}/api/admin/users/1
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create user
POST {{base}}/api/admin/users
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "name": "New User",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Update storage limit
PUT {{base}}/api/admin/users/1/storage-limit
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "storage_limit": 10737418240
}

### Storage overview
GET {{base}}/api/admin/storage/overview
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List configs
GET {{base}}/api/admin/configs
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

